name: extreme_arith_add_commutes_after_if_selected_operand
section: arithmetic-normalization-deep
args: cond:Bool a:Int b:Int c:Int
type: Bool
expect: True
description: Deep arithmetic normalization must preserve integer semantics across direct codegen and helper calls.
law: (= (+ (if {cond} {a} {b}) {c}) (+ {c} (if {cond} {a} {b})))
